  <releases>
    <release version="1.0.5" date="2026-04-14">
      <description>
        <p>First release with AI-native chart rendering:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Mermaid 11 diagrams (lazy-loaded, theme-aware)</li>
          <li>Vega-Lite 5 data visualisations</li>
          <li>Linux default-handler binding via xdg-mime</li>
          <li>Fixed cold-launch render race for file-association opens</li>
          <li>CSS containment reduces scroll CPU on chart-heavy documents</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
